track.name: Hello (feat. A Boogie wit da Hoodie)

wiki.summary: “Hello” was first announced by Pop Smoke’s manager Steven Victor, through his Twitter account. He indicated that this song would be on the deluxe version of Shoot for the Stars Aim for the Moon. During the week ending March 20, 2021, “Hello” peaked at #84 on the Hot 100. Read more on Last.fm.
